manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup] flag is missing.
manifest_analysis.desc: The flag [android:allowBackup] should be set to false. By default it is set to true and allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup] flag is missing.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.google.android.play.core.missingsplits.PlayCoreMissingSplitsActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

manifest_analysis.title:
Service (androidx.work.impl.background.systemjob.SystemJobService) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.BIND_JOB_SERVICE
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

playstore_details.title: Currency converter, convert money & cryptocurrency
playstore_details.description:
Currency Converter 

Money Converter is a handy MUST-HAVE calculator for the businessmen or travellers: convert the price of an item you're going to buy, negotiate your exchange rate easily... And this tool is working OFFLINE :)

Currency Calculator - KEY FEATURES
✓ A calculator
✓ 🕵️  Search currency
✓ 💵 Support over 220 currencies
✓ ✈️ Works offline
✓ Friendly and intuitive user interface
✓ A large entry field for a quick currency search
✓ Currencies exchange rates are updated at every application launch 
✓ Function to switch currencies with a single click

💵 This money converter has more than 170 currencies
 US Dollar (USD), Euro (EUR), Pound Sterling (GBP), Canadian Dollar (CAD), Swiss Franc (CHF), Australian (AUD), Japanese Yen (JPY), Indian Rupee (INR), Chinese Yuan (CNY), Uae Dirham (AED), Afghan Afghani (AFN), Albanian Lek (ALL), Armenian Dram (AMD), Netherlands Antillian Guilder (ANG)... and many more in the money converter

All local currency around the world. Convert all money possible everything. This ultimate travel currency converter.

Help us

Keep in mind that this application is constantly evolving. Got an idea for improvement? 
Can't find something? Please, send me an email to olivier@oworld.fr 

I look forward to your thoughts. Help us make this app the best currency converter.
